tf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='580'%20height='400'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"580\" data-rawheight=\"400\" data-size=\"normal\" data-thumbnail=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-54e08a58465188f02f7beb212fbf0705_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"580\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-54e08a58465188f02f7beb212fbf0705_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-54e08a58465188f02f7beb212fbf0705_b.gif\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563225772,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563225772","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546206555,"updated_time":1546206555,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003eemmmm\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e能证明哥德巴赫\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你没意识到一件事\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这件事到底说明了什么\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e说明你已经是一个成熟的数学工作者了\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e说真的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你已经达到国内甚至世界顶级数学教授的水平了\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那时候\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e就算北大求着你去\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你也不会去的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e因为你会觉得很难受很不自由\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你根本不稀罕学位和名校不名校了\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你唯一想的就是怎么做数学了\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我猜那时候清北会可以特批一个博士学位\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然后聘你为特聘研究员\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果接下来你还有非常出色的工作\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那时候申基金申院士申各种奖项也就顺理成章了\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其实可以参考两个人\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个是中南大学刘路 \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个是张益唐\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e至于有人说直接院士长江\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e各种正教授\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我认为是不可能的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e肯定会给你个最高级的临时职位\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e哈佛普林斯顿也会给你这种职位\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但接下来的路还是靠你自己\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果你真的牛逼到天上\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e再搞出点什么\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然后各路大佬你也拜过了\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e认了山头\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那时候才开始会评长江杰青院士吧\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然后各种正教授博导\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果这种最高级的临时职位\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e五年你都没啥成果\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e大佬们也就把你当个屁放了吧\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563089394,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"80b772cd404e9af2f2ded2996d0bcf09","url_token":"lin-ze-yu-44-13","name":"猴爵","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-fb7993913ea7e99f580a955428ced929_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-fb7993913ea7e99f580a955428ced929_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/80b772cd404e9af2f2ded2996d0bcf09","user_type":"people","headline":"一个同时使用小米和华为的小猴子和爵士","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563089394","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546180494,"updated_time":1546180556,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我觉得哥猜会被一个高中生解出来的概率，比六老师的《敢问路在何方》明年下半年会上映的概率还要小。\u003c/p\u003e","relatio